{"text_id":145143,"tokens":["Seeking"," advice"," from"," multiple"," sources"," is"," vastly"," superior"," to"," relying"," on"," the"," advice"," of"," a"," single"," person","."," This"," approach"," offers"," numerous"," benefits",","," including"," a"," well","-","rounded"," perspective",","," mitigated"," biases",","," and"," increased"," confidence"," in"," decision","-","making","."," Rely","ing"," on"," a"," single"," person","'","s"," advice"," can"," lead"," to"," narrow","-","mindedness",","," missed"," opportunities",","," and"," poor"," decision","-","making",".","\n\n","One"," of"," the"," primary"," benefits"," of"," seeking"," advice"," from"," multiple"," sources"," is"," the"," diverse"," range"," of"," perspectives"," it"," offers","."," When"," an"," individual"," seeks"," advice"," from"," multiple"," people",","," they"," receive"," a"," wealth"," of"," insights",","," experiences",","," and"," expertise","."," For"," instance",","," if"," an"," entrepreneur"," is"," considering"," launching"," a"," new"," product",","," seeking"," advice"," from"," a"," marketing"," expert",","," a"," financial"," analyst",","," and"," a"," product"," designer"," can"," provide"," a"," comprehensive"," understanding"," of"," the"," market",","," financial"," implications",","," and"," design"," requirements","."," This"," collective"," advice"," enables"," the"," entrepreneur"," to"," make"," a"," well","-","informed"," decision",","," taking"," into"," account"," the"," various"," facets"," of"," the"," product"," launch",".","\n\n","Moreover",","," relying"," on"," a"," single"," person","'","s"," advice"," can"," lead"," to"," biased"," opinions","."," A"," single"," advisor"," may"," have"," a"," skewed"," perspective",","," influenced"," by"," their"," personal"," experiences",","," values",","," or"," interests","."," This"," bias"," can"," result"," in"," poor"," decision","-","making",","," as"," it"," is"," based"," on"," a"," limited"," and"," pote